verbose_text: Similarly, we found that ostrich OASL (oOASL), representing ancient avian OASLs, significantly inhibited the replication of CK/0513 virus in DF1 cells, supporting that avian OASLs play a critical role in the immune response to influenza A viruses, similarly to some mammalian OASLs.
